 * Exempel på att kasta en @ref Sten: `` var cell = getCellToUseChip(CHIP_ROCK, fiende)
 * moveTowardCell(cell) useChip(CHIP_ROCK, fiende) ``
 *
 * @category fight
 * @cost 38080 ops
 *
 * @param[in] chip
 * @param[in] entity
 * @param[in] ignoredCells (frivillig)
 * @return cell
 */
function getCellToUseChip(integer|real chip, integer|real entity, Array<integer> ignoredCells) => integer;
function getCellToUseChip(integer|real chip, integer|real entity) => integer;

/**
